    • constructProbabilityMap

      public void constructProbabilityMap​(int pirateProb, int weatherProb, int rescueProb)
      Takes probabilities (out of 100), and constructs the map that shows the probability of each RandomEvent.
      Parameters:
      pirateProb - int for the probability of pirates attacking on this route.
      weatherProb - int for the probability of encountering bad weather on this route.
      rescueProb - int for the probability of coming across sailors that need rescuing on this route.
